metadata.name: Feline Enigma X GM
metadata.description: Despite my love for street photography, the allure and expressive power of the human form always held a special place in my heart. Feline Enigma my first minted nude photograph that won several prestigious awards like FIAP MENTION in AFAD 2nd International Photography Contest. Collaborating with talented Sercan, a typography and 3D abstract artist, we crafted a mesmerizing black and white composition with a GM touch for the Culture!!
